WEBVTT

00:00:00.800 --> 00:00:04.360
So why do you think
the rich should pay more in taxes?

00:00:04.400 --> 00:00:06.776
Why did you buy the latest iPhone?

00:00:06.800 --> 00:00:09.256
Why did you pick your current partner?

00:00:09.280 --> 00:00:12.696
And why did so many people
vote for Donald Trump?

00:00:12.720 --> 00:00:15.240
What were the reasons, why did they do it?

00:00:15.990 --> 00:00:18.096
So we ask this kind
of question all the time,

00:00:18.120 --> 00:00:19.856
and we expect to get an answer.

00:00:19.880 --> 00:00:23.016
And when being asked,
we expect ourselves to know the answer,

00:00:23.040 --> 00:00:25.520
to simply tell why we did as we did.

00:00:26.440 --> 00:00:28.160
But do we really know why?

00:00:29.000 --> 00:00:32.456
